Rayman has been shrunk to the size of an ant! To undo this spell, insects, mushrooms, leaves, and other plants will be your allies as you find your way through a wonderful, macro-photographic world.

From a gorgeous river to a spider nest or the deep recesses of a tree, Rayman Mini thrusts players into a rich, natural environment through exciting 48 levels.

Rayman Mini is a runner platforming game for the whole family! It offers a fun, fast-paced experience that lets players set their own pace. Go for a simple run or try the challenge of getting the perfect score!

To get through this super-sized world, it‚Äôs all about getting the right rhythm in the quest for the perfect flow. Use your honed reflexes, memorize the maps and replay the level as many times as you want‚Ä¶ who knows, you might just find some hidden secrets!

apps.localizedDescription:
In Bridge Constructor+ you have to prove yourself as an accomplished master bridge builder. Play 40 different levels, and build bridges over deep valleys, canals, and rivers. Stress tests reveal whether the bridge you build can withstand the daily stress of continual use from cars, trucks and, more recently, super-heavy tank trucks.





You can choose from a range of materials for each individual bridge, such as wood, steel, cables, or concrete pillars. Use the appropriate materials and stay within budget to build the perfect bridge. The choice of different materials means that there are numerous solutions and approaches and you can build each bridge in any number of ways ‚Äì your budget is the only limit. The refined grid system allows you to realise your idea of the perfect bridge with even more precision. Let your imagination and creativity run free! And if you happen to run into a dead end, you can pick up valuable tips from the help system!



Including awesome Add-Ons: SlopeMania & Trains

In the SlopeMania add-on you find yourself on the Tiltin Islands, home to three brand new islands where you'll even be building your bridges inside colorful grottoes! The 24 tricky, never-before-seen levels will have you using sloping lanes to overcome the massive height differences. The "Crazy Levels" are the real brainteasers and require out-of-the-box thinking and unusual solutions.



Visit the Choonited Kingdom island group in the Trains add-on, with a total of 18 new levels across three islands. Build massive bridges that can withstand the enormous weight of the two new vehicles on offer ‚Äì a commuter train and a heavily loaded freight train. The idyllic and beautifully designed landscapes will make the heart of every railroad fanatic skip a beat.




FEATURES:

‚Ä¢ 40 Levels on the island nation of Camatuga

‚Ä¢ Free build mode and help system

‚Ä¢ 5 Settings: city, canyon, beach, mountains, hills

‚Ä¢ Improved grid system

‚Ä¢ Map with unlocked worlds/levels

‚Ä¢ 4 different building materials: wood, steel, cables, concrete pillars

‚Ä¢ Color coded load indicator for different building materials

‚Ä¢ Three different load bearing levels: car, truck and tank truck

‚Ä¢ High score per level






FEATURES SlopeMania Add-On

‚Ä¢ Completely new Tiltin Islands

‚Ä¢ Option to build sloping roads ‚Äì even for Camatuga

‚Ä¢ Additional "Grotto" setting

‚Ä¢ 24 "sloping" levels inc. especially tricky "Crazy Levels"

‚Ä¢ Explosive tank truck as an exciting new vehicle




FEATURES Trains Add-On

‚Ä¢ Open up 3 new islands with 18 new levels.

‚Ä¢ Build bridges for modern commuter trains and heavy freight trains!

‚Ä¢ New scenery: Enjoy the view of picturesque mountains and ravines!

apps.localizedDescription:
Have you ever been stuck in traffic and wished you could do something to fix it? In Mini Motorways, the city‚Äôs traffic problems are in your hands.

From the makers of Mini Metro, Mini Motorways is a game about drawing the roads that drive a growing city. Build a road network, one road at a time, to create a bustling metropolis. Redesign your city to keep the traffic flowing, and carefully manage upgrades to meet the changing demands. How long can you keep the cities of the world moving?

Features:

‚Ä¢ Draw roads in dynamic cities that grow and change - every game is unique!

‚Ä¢ Explore stunning maps inspired by cities all around the world.

‚Ä¢ Choose from a variety of upgrades to meet the demands of your ever-expanding road network: highways, roundabouts, and more!

‚Ä¢ Stress-free Endless Mode offers you a relaxing gameplay experience, plus you can continue building your city after Game Over.

‚Ä¢ Tackle our Expert Mode, which features twists such as permanent roads and limited upgrades for the ultimate challenge.

‚Ä¢ Select different colour palettes on every map including colourblind and night modes.

‚Ä¢ Relax to a responsive soundtrack from Disasterpeace that grows along with your city.

‚Ä¢ Unlock new maps and achievements as you achieve mastery.

‚Ä¢ Export GIFs of your city layouts to share with your friends.

‚Ä¢ Compete against other players in Daily and Weekly Challenges.

‚Ä¢ Compatible with Siri Remote, Bluetooth and MFi controllers.
apps.name: Mini Motorways
apps.subtitle: Draw roads that drive the city
apps.versionDescription:
Sea to Sky Update

Pack your umbrella and hiking boots because we're off to Vancouver in our latest update to Mini Motorways! Nestled amongst the rugged Canadian coast of British Columbia, this coastal metropolis is home to narrow waterways, rugged mountains and lush parks. It‚Äôs up to you how you manage the city‚Äôs unique geography to keep the traffic along these Maple Motorways.

This update to Mini Motorways includes:

‚Ä¢ A brand new map! Take a trip to the west coast of Canada and explore the highly-requested city of Vancouver, our latest Mini Motorways map.

‚Ä¢ New Achievements, Daily Challenges, Weekly Challenges, and City Challenges.

‚Ä¢ Various minor bug fixes and performance improvements.

Nulls Royale is a private server for Clash Royale, a popular mobile game developed by Supercell. It offers various features and advantages for players compared to the official game servers.

Function:

Private Server: Null's Royale operates on separate servers independent of the official Clash Royale servers.

Modified Gameplay: It provides modified features, including unlimited gems, gold, cards, and chests.

Custom Events: Null's Royale introduces unique and customized events not available in the official game.
Characteristics:

Unlimited Resources: Players can access unlimited gems, gold, and cards, enabling them to level up and progress faster.

Custom Cards: Null's Royale features exclusive cards that are not available in the original game, allowing for a diverse and customized gameplay experience.

Real-time Battles: Users can engage in real-time battles with other players on the private server.

Stable and Secure: The server is designed to provide a stable and secure gaming environment without any significant connectivity issues or security risks.
Highlights:

Exclusive Content: The private server gives players access to exclusive cards and features not found in the official game, making gameplay more exciting and unpredictable.

Faster Progression: With unlimited resources, players can upgrade cards and unlock new content at a much faster pace, allowing them to reach higher levels more quickly.

Customized Gameplay: Null's Royale offers modified events and gameplay mechanics, providing a fresh and unique experience compared to the original Clash Royale.
Advantages:

Enhanced Gameplay: The ability to access unlimited resources and unique content adds a new dimension to the game, making it more enjoyable and compelling.

Quicker Progress: Null's Royale enables players to progress faster, eliminating the need to spend significant time or money on in-app purchases.

Experimentation and Testing: The private server allows players to try out different strategies, card combinations, and game features without any limitations or risks.
